<chapter xml:id="ch-01-dim-analysis-uncertainties" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Dimensional Analysis and Uncertainties</title>

  <introduction>
    <p>
      Before we can start discussing the interesting stuff, we need to understand how we think about quantities and measurements.
      This chapter is meant to be a brief introduction to dimensional analysis and uncertainties, which are two important tools that every scientist should be familiar with.
    </p>
  </introduction>
